lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Brian went to Punjab on his holiday
He heard the music and he started to sway
With dhol beats and catchy tunes, he couldn't resist
Now he's dancing like crazy, happiness in his wrist

[Chorus]
Dancing in Punjab, oh what a delight
Brian moves his feet, filling the night
With laughter and joy, the celebration begins
Punjabis and Brian, dancing with grins
